<div class="chapter ch1" data-usfm="PSA.1">
  <div class="label">1</div>
  <div class="ms">
    <span class="heading">诗篇卷一</span>
  </div>
  <div class="s">
    <span class="heading">真福</span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="content"> </span><span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.1.1"><span class="label">1</span><span
      class="content">不从恶人的计谋，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.1.1"><span class="content">不站罪人的道路，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.1.1"><span class="content">不坐亵慢人的座位，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.1.1"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v2"
      data-usfm="PSA.1.2"><span class="label">2</span><span class="content">惟喜爱耶和华的律法，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="PSA.1.2"><span class="content">昼夜思想，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="PSA.1.2"><span class="content">这人便为有福！</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="PSA.1.2"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v3"
      data-usfm="PSA.1.3"><span class="label">3</span><span class="content">他要像一棵树栽在溪水旁，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.1.3"><span class="content">按时候结果子，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.1.3"><span class="content">叶子也不枯干。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.1.3"><span class="content">凡他所做的尽都顺利。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="b"></div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.1.3"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v4"
      data-usfm="PSA.1.4"><span class="label">4</span><span class="content">恶人并不是这样，</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="PSA.1.4"><span class="content">乃像糠秕被风吹散。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="PSA.1.4"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v5"
      data-usfm="PSA.1.5"><span class="label">5</span><span class="content">因此，当审判的时候、恶人必站立不住；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="PSA.1.5"><span class="content">罪人在义人的会中也是如此。</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="PSA.1.5"><span class="content"> </span></span><span class="verse v6"
      data-usfm="PSA.1.6"><span class="label">6</span><span class="content">因为耶和华知道义人的道路；</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="q1">
    <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="PSA.1.6"><span class="content">恶人的道路却必灭亡。</span></span>
  </div>
</div>
